{"word":"διατέμνω","slug":"διατέμνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διατέμνω</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-τάμνω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-τεμῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to cut through, cut in twain, dissever</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>δίχα δ.</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to disunite</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to cut up</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>διατμηθῆναι λέπαδνα</el> <i>to be cut into</i> strips, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}